overview.en: GPG focuses on public chain projects for the commercial application of the encrypted digital asset industry. Based on the blockchain network for global collaboration, it provides global users with accurate decentralized intelligent futures blockchain technology for digital asset issuance, trading, and management related services.
overview.zh: GPG专注于加密数字资产行业商业应用的公有链项目，基于区块链网络进行全球协同，并为全球用户精准提供数字资产发行、交易及管理相关服务的去中心化的智能期货区块链技术。
